    <p>Please refer to previous post:  <a href="http://rolandtanglao.com/2020/10/30/p1-switched-to-ubuntu-server-bionic-compiled-rstudio-but-plots-do-not-work/">Switched  from Buster to Ubuntu Server Bionic Beaver and compiled RStudio Server  and it all works except for plots, need type=‚Äôcairo‚Äô and or xvfb-run</a></p>
